//TEXT
<jaT0001>That monster was no longer "Aizawa Shuhei". The consciousness of the man who loved this girl... was fast asleep, deep inside this monster.
<enT0001>That monster was no longer "Aizawa Shuhei". The consciousness of the man who loved this girl... was fast asleep, deep inside this monster.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>One couldn't call that tragic either... because it meant that he didn't have to witness the horrible deeds he was about to commit.
<enT0002>One couldn't call that tragic either... because it meant that he didn't have to witness the horrible deeds he was about to commit.

//TEXT
<jaT0003>He didn't have to watch as he tore apart the person he loved most in this world.
<enT0003>He didn't have to watch as he tore apart the person he loved most in this world.

//TEXT
<jaT0004>You should close your eyes. You should avert your eyes from the horrible tragedy that's about to occur.
<enT0004>You should close your eyes. You should avert your eyes from the horrible tragedy that's about to occur.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0005>"Hii! N-No..."
<enT0005>"Hii! N-No..."

//TEXT
<jaT0006>Pressed down by the blob of slime, the girl screamed in fear. However... that creature refused to stop.
<enT0006>Pressed down by the blob of slime, the girl screamed in fear. However... that creature refused to stop.

//TEXT
<jaT0007>"He" was merely a manipulated doll now, nothing more than a puppet following someone's deadly intent.
<enT0007>"He" was merely a manipulated doll now, nothing more than a puppet following someone's deadly intent.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0008>"No, don't, Shuhei-kun... Get control of yourself..."
<enT0008>"No, don't, Shuhei-kun... Get control of yourself..."

//TEXT
<jaT0009>No matter how often she cried out, her plea couldn't reach him. Still, the girl continued to call out to him.
<enT0009>No matter how often she cried out, her plea couldn't reach him. Still, the girl continued to call out to him.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0010>"No, don't... Shuhei-kun, don't do it... hah, hah... Stop it, Shuhei-kun..."
<enT0010>"No, don't... Shuhei-kun, don't do it... hah, hah... Stop it, Shuhei-kun..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0011>"*sniffle*...No, Shuhei-kun... you can't do this..."
<enT0011>"*sniffle*...No, Shuhei-kun... you can't do this..."

//TEXT
<jaT0012>......
<enT0012>......

//TEXT
<jaT0013>Was it a miracle? As if responding to her cries, the slimy creature stopped for just one moment.
<enT0013>Was it a miracle? As if responding to her cries, the slimy creature stopped for just one moment.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0014>"Shuhei, kun? Have you regained..."
<enT0014>"Shuhei, kun? Have you regained..."

//TEXT
<jaT0015>As the girl's face glimmered with joy, the someone manipulating Shuhei-kun was probably scoffing.
<enT0015>As the girl's face glimmered with joy, the someone manipulating Shuhei-kun was probably scoffing.

//TEXT
<jaT0016>After giving them hope, tear them apart without mercy. That was someone's favorite method.
<enT0016>After giving them hope, tear them apart without mercy. That was someone's favorite method.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0017>"Ah, no..."
<enT0017>"Ah, no..."

//TEXT
<jaT0018>As the slimy creature began to move again, the girl cried out in despair. However... she held absolute faith in the person who held that creature's former body.
<enT0018>As the slimy creature began to move again, the girl cried out in despair. However... she held absolute faith in the person who held that creature's former body.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0019>"Ahh, no... don't do it, Shuhei-kun..."
<enT0019>"Ahh, no... don't do it, Shuhei-kun..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0020>"Ah, no, no..."
<enT0020>"Ah, no, no..."

//TEXT
<jaT0021>No matter what he looks like, no matter what he does to her... the girl simply continued to call his name.
<enT0021>No matter what he looks like, no matter what he does to her... the girl simply continued to call his name.

//TEXT
<jaT0022>However, that monster... tore her faith apart, along with everything else.
<enT0022>However, that monster... tore her faith apart, along with everything else.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0023>"...N-no!"
<enT0023>"...N-no!"

//TEXT
<jaT0024>With his terrible brute force, he ripped the girl's clothes to shreds. She screamed, but still... she cared for that former man.
<enT0024>With his terrible brute force, he ripped the girl's clothes to shreds. She screamed, but still... she cared for that former man.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0025>"Nn, Shuhei-kun..."
<enT0025>"Nn, Shuhei-kun..."

//TEXT
<jaT0026>Her eyes were filled with tears, but still she worried about that man. Even as the creepy slime crawled over her bare skin, she held her voice in check.
<enT0026>Her eyes were filled with tears, but still she worried about that man. Even as the creepy slime crawled over her bare skin, she held her voice in check.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0027>"Nnn... Nn, Ngg... please stop, I'm scared..."
<enT0027>"Nnn... Nn, Ngg... please stop, I'm scared..."

//TEXT
<jaT0028>She was so frightened goose bumps covered her skin. However, she didn't resist. She just lay there, accepting his actions.
<enT0028>She was so frightened goose bumps covered her skin. However, she didn't resist. She just lay there, accepting his actions.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0029>"Nn, Ngg, hah..."
<enT0029>"Nn, Ngg, hah..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0030>"Nn, hah... Shuhei-kun, Shuhei-kun..."
<enT0030>"Nn, hah... Shuhei-kun, Shuhei-kun..."

//TEXT
<jaT0031>The girl continued to endure the eerie sensation on her skin. ...Then it grew worse.
<enT0031>The girl continued to endure the eerie sensation on her skin. ...Then it grew worse.

//TEXT
<jaT0032>The slimy creature moved towards her lower body... and began sliding deep into her secret spot.
<enT0032>The slimy creature moved towards her lower body... and began sliding deep into her secret spot.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0033>"Kya! Aah!....Aahh.... ahh... ahh.... ahh..."
<enT0033>"Kya! Aah!....Aahh.... ahh... ahh.... ahh..."

//TEXT
<jaT0034>Her voice cracked in pain.
<enT0034>Her voice cracked in pain.

//TEXT
<jaT0035>Because she was trying to endure, it was only a suppressed cry. Any other girl would be screaming from the intense pain.
<enT0035>Because she was trying to endure, it was only a suppressed cry. Any other girl would be screaming from the intense pain.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0036>"Ahh, Nng..."
<enT0036>"Ahh, Nng..."

//TEXT
<jaT0037>She was in pain from having something forced into the place she had never let anyone enter before.
<enT0037>She was in pain from having something forced into the place she had never let anyone enter before.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0038>"Hah, hah, Hnn... Ngg, ahh..."
<enT0038>"Hah, hah, Hnn... Ngg, ahh..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0039>"Ngg, ngg... Nggha... ah... ah..."
<enT0039>"Ngg, ngg... Nggha... ah... ah..."

//TEXT
<jaT0040>Her body was soaked in sweat as it quivered in fear.
<enT0040>Her body was soaked in sweat as it quivered in fear.

//TEXT
<jaT0041>After it came this far, even she couldn't stop from screaming.
<enT0041>After it came this far, even she couldn't stop from screaming.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0042>"Agghh! Agghh..."
<enT0042>"Agghh! Agghh..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0043>"Ng, agh, hah, hah, hah... Nggh..."
<enT0043>"Ng, agh, hah, hah, hah... Nggh..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0044>"Nggha..."
<enT0044>"Nggha..."

//TEXT
<jaT0045>After an extremely brief remission, the monster inside her vagina moved onwards, reaching her deepest depths.
<enT0045>After an extremely brief remission, the monster inside her vagina moved onwards, reaching her deepest depths.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0046>"Aaggh! Ah, aggh...... Ngh, HYAAAA!"
<enT0046>"Aaggh! Ah, aggh...... Ngh, HYAAAA!"

//TEXT
<jaT0047>Even in her despair... she held faith in her beloved. As large tears spilled from her eyes, she desperately called out his name.
<enT0047>Even in her despair... she held faith in her beloved. As large tears spilled from her eyes, she desperately called out his name.

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0048>"Shuhei, kun..."
<enT0048>"Shuhei, kun..."

//TEXT 【Nao】
<jaT0049>"Shuhei-kun..."
<enT0049>"Shuhei-kun..."

//TEXT
<jaT0050>......
<enT0050>......

//TEXT
<jaT0051>...
<enT0051>...

